## HQ KVM SNMPD Config File

com2sec local     localhost       challcmon
com2sec theworld  default         challcmon

group   MyRWGroup  v1              local
group   MyROGroup  v1             theworld

view all    included  .1                               80

access MyROGroup ""      any       noauth    exact      all    none   none
access MyRWGroup ""      any       noauth    exact      all    all    none

syslocation CHA HQ
syscontact Root <root@localhost> (configure /etc/snmp/snmp.local.conf)

proc cupsd 1 1


disk / 1000000000

disk /var/lib/libvirt/DB-Store 1000000000
disk /var/lib/libvirt/DB-Store2 1000000000
disk /var/lib/libvirt/ISO_Repo 1000000000
disk /var/lib/libvirt/Tools 1000000000
disk /var/lib/libvirt/VM_OS_Storage 1000000000
disk /var/lib/libvirt/VM_Storage 1000000000